Same. Job's getting worse.

633
01:10:28,800 --> 01:10:30,820
Can't change the world on your own.

634
01:10:31,600 --> 01:10:32,580
What choice do I have?

635
01:10:34,490 --> 01:10:35,570
When you're too busy swimming.

636
01:10:37,170 --> 01:10:40,610
Rachel, all of... all this...

637
01:10:43,010 --> 01:10:44,570
It's not me.

638
01:10:45,550 --> 01:10:49,080
It's... inside. I am...

639
01:11:00,310 --> 01:11:06,370
Bruce, deep down you may still be that same great kid you used to be.

640
01:11:09,050 --> 01:11:10,250
But it's not who you are underneath.

641
01:11:12,050 --> 01:11:13,550
It's what you do that defines you.

642
01:11:26,060 --> 01:11:27,990
Dr. Crane, thanks for coming.

643
01:11:28,090 --> 01:11:30,790
Not at all. He cut his wrists.

644
01:11:31,190 --> 01:11:32,810
Probably looking for the insanity plea.

645
01:11:33,450 --> 01:11:34,810
But if anything should happen...

646
01:11:34,810 --> 01:11:36,730
Of course. Better safe than sorry.

647
01:11:41,340 --> 01:11:42,480
Yeah, Dr. Crane.

648
01:11:42,740 --> 01:11:44,640
I can't take it anymore. It's all too much.

649
01:11:44,660 --> 01:11:46,120
The walls are closing in.

650
01:11:46,400 --> 01:11:47,140
Blah, blah, blah.

651
01:11:48,120 --> 01:11:50,540
A couple of days of this food will be true.

652
01:11:51,660 --> 01:11:52,060
