657
01:12:02,540 --> 01:12:05,940
and I know about your experiments with the inmates of your nuthouse.

658
01:12:07,160 --> 01:12:10,140
See, I don't go into business with a guy without finding out his dirty secrets.

659
01:12:11,120 --> 01:12:15,960
