663
01:12:32,390 --> 01:12:33,910
Even he can't get me in here.

664
01:12:34,670 --> 01:12:35,510
Not in my town.

665
01:12:41,650 --> 01:12:43,050
Would you like to see my mask?

666
01:12:44,910 --> 01:12:46,130
I use it in my experiments.

667
01:12:47,030 --> 01:12:53,140
It's probably not very frightening to a guy like you.

668
01:12:53,900 --> 01:12:56,140
But these crazies, they can't stand it.

669
01:12:57,550 --> 01:12:59,350
So when did the nut take over the nut house?

670
01:13:00,310 --> 01:13:02,490
They scream and they cry.

671
01:13:04,070 --> 01:13:05,070
Which is your game now?

672
01:13:05,130 --> 01:13:10,710
He's not faking. Not that one.

673
01:13:11,580 --> 01:13:15,240
I'll talk to the judge and see if I can get him moved to the secure wing at Arkham.

674
01:13:15,260 --> 01:13:16,580
