675
01:13:45,750 --> 01:13:48,350
The scum is getting jumpy because you stood up to Falcone.

676
01:13:48,990 --> 01:13:49,610
It's a start.

677
01:13:50,110 --> 01:13:51,850
Your partner was at the docks with Falcone.

678
01:13:52,690 --> 01:13:55,150
Oh, he moonlights as a low-level enforcer.

679
01:13:55,710 --> 01:13:57,120
They were splitting the shipment in two.

680
01:13:57,120 --> 01:13:58,670
Only half went to the dealers.

681
01:13:59,710 --> 01:14:01,330
Why? What about the other half?

682
01:14:01,990 --> 01:14:02,610
Vlas knows.

683
01:14:03,030 --> 01:14:03,670
He won't talk.

684
01:14:05,170 --> 01:14:05,930
He'll talk to me.

685
01:14:06,910 --> 01:14:09,650
Mission Alive set up a massive task force to catch you.

686
01:14:10,330 --> 01:14:11,370
He thinks you're dangerous.

687
01:14:12,070 --> 01:14:12,710
What do you think?

688
01:14:14,720 --> 01:14:23,070
I think you're trying to help, but I've been wrong before.

689
01:14:35,250 --> 01:14:37,110
I have kids to feed.

690
01:14:37,570 --> 01:14:38,570
Well, I don't like falafel.

691
01:14:55,170 --> 01:14:56,630
Where were the other drugs going?

692
01:14:57,830 --> 01:14:58,750
I never knew.

693
01:14:59,230 --> 01:14:59,790
I don't know.

694
01:15:00,490 --> 01:15:01,330
I swear to God.

695
01:15:01,490 --> 01:15:02,010
Swear to me!

696
01:15:08,590 --> 01:15:09,350
I don't know.

697
01:15:09,850 --> 01:15:10,390
I never knew.

698
01:15:10,990 --> 01:15:11,150
Never.

699
01:15:11,730 --> 01:15:14,870
They went to some guy for a couple of days before they went to the dealer.

700
01:15:15,030 --> 01:15:15,170
Why?

701
