732
01:20:26,070 --> 01:20:30,610
I analyzed your blood, isolating the receptor compounds in the protein-based catalyst.

733
01:20:31,230 --> 01:20:32,990
That meant I understand any of that.

734
01:20:33,110 --> 01:20:36,690
Not at all. I just wanted you to know how hard it was.

735
01:20:37,250 --> 01:20:39,530
Bottom line, I synthesized an antidote.

736
01:20:39,770 --> 01:20:40,490
Could you make more?

737
01:20:40,970 --> 01:20:43,010
You planning on gassing yourself again, Mr. Wayne?

738
01:20:43,510 --> 01:20:47,070
You know how it is, Mr. Fox. You're out at night looking for kicks.

739
01:20:47,270 --> 01:20:49,690
