758
01:21:34,700 --> 01:21:36,110
Get Crane down there right now.

759
01:21:36,250 --> 01:21:37,490
Do not take no for an answer.

760
01:21:37,630 --> 01:21:40,930
Call Dr. Lehman and tell him we'll need our own assessment on the judge's desk by morning.

761
01:21:41,610 --> 01:21:42,150
