764
01:21:46,510 --> 01:21:47,350
You're going to Arkham now?

765
01:21:47,830 --> 01:21:48,990
It's in the narrows, Rachel.

766
01:21:50,640 --> 01:21:51,700
You enjoy your party, Bruce.

767
01:21:52,680 --> 01:21:53,800
Some of us have work to do.

768
01:21:54,440 --> 01:21:55,020
