773
01:23:10,850 --> 01:23:11,750
I need some information.

774
01:23:12,370 --> 01:23:13,590
The Wayne and the...

775
01:23:14,150 --> 01:23:16,590
47B-1ME.

776
01:23:20,000 --> 01:23:21,000
It's a microwave emitter.

777
01:23:21,000 --> 01:23:23,580
It was designed to vaporize an enemy's water supply.

778
01:23:24,020 --> 01:23:28,330
Rumor was they tested dispersing water-based chemical agents into the air,

779
01:23:28,330 --> 01:23:30,000
