780
01:23:32,070 --> 01:23:36,230
I want all the information on the development of this project.

781
01:23:36,290 --> 01:23:40,290
All data, files, backup disks on my desk right away.

782
01:23:40,990 --> 01:23:41,690
Did you lose one?

783
01:23:43,700 --> 01:23:45,700
I'm merging your department with Archives.

784
01:24:16,870 --> 01:24:20,660
This is most irregular. I have nothing further to add to the report I filed with the judge.

785
01:24:20,660 --> 01:24:22,290
